---
title: Saucy Plum and Ginger Beef Meatballs with Green Onion Rice and Veggies
description: Juicy ginger and garlic beef meatballs get tossed in a plum sauce spiked with soy for an explosion of fragrant, savoury-sweet flavour! This umami-packed meal is sure to be a hit with the whole family!
